- tested with xchat version 2.8.8

INSTALLATION

- copy xchat-speak.py and pronouciation_database.pickle to ~/.xchat2

if two folks post at the same time, both are spoken concurrently.

COMMANDS IN XCHAT

/mute [speaker] Stop speaking everything in a channel or private message, or mute a specific speaker in all channels.
/unmute [speaker] Start speaking everything in a channel or private message, or unmute a specific speaker in all channels.

BUGS
- had lots of aplay processes build up at start once, one for each message
